query:
SELECT
    "timestamp",
    CASE
        WHEN $1 = 1 THEN wind_speed_10m
        WHEN $1 = 2 THEN air_temperature_2m
        WHEN $1 = 3 THEN relative_humidity_2m
        WHEN $1 = 4 THEN air_pressure_at_sea_level
        WHEN $1 = 5 THEN precipitation_amount
    END AS "bytes!"
FROM
    weather_images
WHERE
    "timestamp" = $2::TIMESTAMPTZ
